To install amis:

./configure
make
make install

This will install amis in /usr/local/bin/.

If you want to install it in another directory:

./configure --prefix=XXX
make
make install

This will install amis in XXX/bin/.

If you cannot find "configure" script, run the following command first:

aclocal; autoheader; automake --add-missing --foreign; autoconf

Then, follow the above instructions.

